<li>Period period 2</li>
<li>Element category: alkali metal</li>
<li>Electron configuration: 2s1</li>
<li>Per shell: 2, 1</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Physical properties</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Phase: solid</li>
<li>Melting point: 453.65 K ​(180.50 °C, ​356.90 °F)</li>
<li>Boiling point: 1603 K ​(1330 °C, ​2426 °F)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>History</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Discovery: Johan August Arfwedson (1817)</li>
<li>First isolation: William Thomas Brande (1821)</li>
</ul>
